135
00:15:57,759 --> 00:16:01,759
[SPEAKER_00] Ja Te molim Isuse da u Tvoje sve to ime,

136
00:16:01,759 --> 00:16:05,759
[SPEAKER_00] po našim čežnjama, po našim molitvama,

137
00:16:07,759 --> 00:16:10,759
[SPEAKER_00] dođe Tvoje ozdravljenje, dođe Tvoj dodir,

138
00:16:10,759 --> 00:16:13,759
[SPEAKER_00] da se zalječe duhovne rane.

139
00:16:13,759 --> 00:16:17,759
[SPEAKER_00] Molim Te za sve one koji trpe na duhu gospodina.

140
00:16:17,759 --> 00:16:22,759
[SPEAKER_00] Donesi im slobodu svakog područja i tamo gdje nisu slobodni.

141
00:16:22,759 --> 00:16:26,759
[SPEAKER_00] Daj im oslobođenje od ovisnosti,

142
00:16:26,759 --> 00:16:29,759
[SPEAKER_00] oslobođenje od grijeha.

143
00:16:29,759 --> 00:16:33,759
